fields.name: AuthorizationAudience
fields.description: The aud (audience) the access token was request for. This is the same as what was provided in the listTokens request.

fields.name: ExpiresIn
fields.description: The number of seconds the access token will be valid.

fields.name: ExpiresOn
fields.description: The timespan when the access token expires. This is represented as the number of seconds from epoch.

fields.name: NotBefore
fields.description: The timespan when the access token takes effect. This is represented as the number of seconds from epoch.

fields.name: ResourceId
fields.description: The Azure resource ID for the issued token. This is either the managed application ID or the user-assigned identity ID.
